Hi Narasimha - I had this error today. It has something to do with Terraform no-longer using Block format (the use of '[ ]' in your Route table, and Security group). 

I am no expert, but with some googling I found that if you replace the following:

Route = [ { with Route {
Ingress = [ { with Ingress {
Egress = [ { with Egress {

and remove the closing ] in your code, and you no longer use the opening block [.

This worked for me. Hope it helps!

